The paper deals with the problem of solving reachability-time games on timed automata, which involves both logic and automata theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science). The paper also proposes a strategy improvement algorithm, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with formal languages and automata theory, which are covered in the category of Programming Languages (cs.PL). The paper also discusses the computational complexity of the problem, which falls under the category of Formal Languages and Automata Theory (cs.FL). Finally, the paper deals with timed automata, which are a type of dynamical system, and hence, the paper can also be classified under the category of Systems and Control (cs.SY).
